headline: Equity Residential price target raised to $81 from $80 at JPMorgan
summary: JPMorgan raised the firm’s price target on Equity Residential (EQR) to $81 from $80 and keeps a Neutral rating on the shares. The firm updated residential real estate investment trust models following the Q3 reports. The group is well owned, and JPMorgan sees only average earnings growth over the next couple years with less potential for external growth, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
